Faculty Object manager:

Faculty_ID:Number,Salary:Currency,Department:Picklist(IT,HR,Computer,Mechanical,Civil,ENTC),Joining Date:Date,Email:Email



Validation Rule:

Faculty_Name_Validation:LEN(Name) < 3:Faculty Name must contain at least 3 characters,Faculty_ID_Validation:Faculty_ID__c <= 0:Faculty ID must be greater than 0,

Salary_Validation:OR(Salary__c < 10000,Salary__c > 500000):Salary must be between 10,000 and 500,000,Joining_Date_Validation:Joining_Date__c > TODAY():Joining Date cannot be future date



